HEADWORD: Consopite
<hw>Con"so*pite</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocr⟧n"s⟦osl⟧*p⟦imac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>consopitus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>consopire</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Lulled to sleep.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Dr. H.
